# Quiz
https://pete331.github.io/Quiz/.
This program was created to showcase various javascript objects in various functions to go through a quiz and store scores in local storage. 
It also retrieves scores from local storage with a function to clear these scores.
It access's and appends various html elements. Including hiding and showing various screens all with the one html page.

Once the start button is pressed the timer reduces each second - if a wrong answer is selected 15 seconds are taken from the time.